original_title: Ang Mga Kidnaper Ni Ronnie Lazaro
overview: "ANG MGA KIDNAPER NI RONNIE LAZARO" is about a group of down and out-of-luck men who decided to make a film starring Ronnie Lazaro, the most sought-after indie actor in the Philippines. Things get complicated when Lazaro decides to beg-off from acting on their supposed "indie film" and the guys were forced to abduct the actor." - Agimat Project

production_companies.name: Film Development Council of the Philippines

title: The Kidnappers of Ronnie Lazaro
